407
00:30:15,470 --> 00:30:16,920
and bribe more people.

408
00:30:19,590 --> 00:30:20,680
Keep the money well.

409
00:30:21,190 --> 00:30:22,760
Don't keep it in your residence again.

410
00:30:23,950 --> 00:30:24,920
Don't worry.

411
00:30:25,110 --> 00:30:27,280
