465
00:33:20,710 --> 00:33:22,920
Stop crying. The dishes are getting cold.

466
00:33:23,520 --> 00:33:24,310
Let's eat together.

467
00:33:27,710 --> 00:33:28,310
Okay.

468
00:33:30,310 --> 00:33:31,430
