542
00:37:20,080 --> 00:37:20,760
Definitely.

543
00:37:20,870 --> 00:37:24,470
You're wise, my son-in-law.

544
00:37:43,280 --> 00:37:44,040
Stop.

545
00:37:44,910 --> 00:37:47,190
Sir, this is the customs clearance pass.

546
00:37:49,950 --> 00:37:50,630
Have a look.

